OL,3,CWes Streeting apologises for joke
OL,4,Cabout prisoner releases caught on
OL,5,Cmicrophone
OL,7,FNew Defence Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,8,Fhas apologised for comments he made
OL,9,Fabout the early release of prisoners
OL,10,Fwhich were picked up by a microphone.
OL,12,FStreeting, who was selected in Prime
OL,13,FMinister Andy Burnham's new-look
OL,14,FCabinet on Monday, made the remarks in
OL,15,Fa conversation with Home Secretary
OL,16,FShabana Mahmood and the new Justice
OL,17,FSecretary Alex Norris on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
