OL,3,CWes Streeting apologises for joke
OL,4,Cabout prisoner releases caught on
OL,5,Cmicrophone
OL,7,FShe wrote on X: "I appreciate this is
OL,8,Fan extremely serious issue and do not
OL,9,Fwant anyone to mistake this moment of
OL,10,Flevity for a lack of serious intent."
OL,12,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,13,Fwrote on X: "While Andy Burnham's
OL,14,Fcabinet are joking about letting
OL,15,Fcriminals out of prison early,
OL,16,FConservatives are listening to victims
OL,17,Fand will continue to fight this
OL,18,Fdisgusting policy."
OL,26,@oD@QOUrD@eO]uD@MOUzD@SO]
