OL,3,CWes Streeting apologises for joke
OL,4,Cabout prisoner releases caught on
OL,5,Cmicrophone
OL,7,FUnder the new Sentencing Act, set to
OL,8,Fcome into force in September, around
OL,9,F6,000 criminals are set to be released
OL,10,Funder the early prison release scheme.
OL,12,FAlex Norris has been urged to
OL,13,Freconsider the early release scheme,
OL,14,Fand when asked about reports that the
OL,15,Fprime minister could be working on
OL,16,Fexempting rapists and child groomers,
OL,17,Fhis spokesman said: "The government's
OL,18,Ffully focused on keeping the public
OL,19,Fsafe.
OL,26,@yD@UOU
