OL,3,CWes Streeting apologises for joke
OL,4,Cabout prisoner releases caught on
OL,5,Cmicrophone
OL,7,FStreeting's comments come as the
OL,8,Fmother of police officer Andrew Harper
OL,9,Fsaid it feels like an "insult" that
OL,10,Ftwo of her son's killers may be
OL,11,Feligible for early release from prison.
OL,13,FPC Harper was 28 when he sustained
OL,14,Ffatal injuries while responding to a
OL,15,Fquad bike theft in Sulhamstead,
OL,16,FBerkshire, in August 2019.
OL,26,@qD@WOUqD@^O]
